properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 19 at 11:56AM EST until January 20 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Buffalo NY
properties.description:
* WHAT...Lake effect snow and blowing snow. Additional snow
accumulations of 3 to 5 inches. Winds gusting up to 30 mph will
produce some blowing and drifting snow.

* WHERE...Oswego county, mainly in the western portion of the
county.

* WHEN...Until 4 AM EST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Plan on snow covered and slippery road conditions.
Blowing snow will reduce visibility at times.
properties.instruction:
Periods of snow will result in snow covered roads and limited
visibilities. Slow down and use caution while driving.

Submit snow reports through our website or social media.
